HEADWORD: offsides
<hw>offsides</hw></mhw> <pos>adj.</pos>
<fld>(Sports)</fld> <def>Illegally beyond a prescribed line or area or
ahead of the ball or puck; -- in sports such as football or hockey;
<as>as, the touchdown was nullified because the left tackle was
<ex>offside</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
